Comment: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.34,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Go ask my instincts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.68,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}一直響著的沉默的警鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.68,0:02:47.90,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}那又是誰的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.90,0:02:50.50,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}不要迷茫跳進去跳進去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.86,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}站起來 破壞掉這無理的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:54.45,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}如果解不開這沉默
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:56.87,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}就大喊露鳩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.87,0:02:59.20,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}直到終幕我都要說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.07,OPED_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur3}Gear up! 這不是玩笑
